U-LEACREE unethimba le-R&D eliqeqeshiwe nelifundile.Abanye onjiniyela bezobuchwepheshe banesipiliyoni seminyaka engaphezu kwengu-20 ocwaningweni nasekuthuthukiseni uhlelo lokumiswa kwezimoto.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, inkampani yethu ihlale ibamba imihlangano yokuqeqeshwa kwe-R&D.
Okubaluleke nakakhulu, i-LEACREE ibambisana namanyuvesi asekhaya adumile ocwaningweni nasekuthuthukisweni kobuchwepheshe obumisiwe, njengeBeijing Institute of Technology, iSichuan University Jinjiang College kanyeInyuvesi yaseXihuay.
Ngemva komzamo weminyaka engu-15, sithuthukise ngempumelelo izinto zezimoto ezingaphezu kuka-3000, ezihlanganisa izimoto zabagibeli, ama-SUV, ama-Off-road, izimoto zezentengiselwano, ama-pickup, amaloli amancane nezinye izimoto zamasosha nezimoto ezikhethekile.

Kwenzeke obekungalindelwe muntu amaqembu aKwaZulu-Natal adlala esigabeni esiphezulu ku-Absa Premiership engena wonke kuTop 8 edlalwa amaqembu aphethe isizini ebalwa nayisishiyagalombili aphezulu. Lawa maqembu yi-Maritzburg United eqeqeshwa wuFadlu Davids nelale isine kulogi, iLamontville Golden Arrows eqeqeshwa wuClinton Larsen elale indawo yesikhombisa kanye neqembu i-AmaZulu FC eliqeqeshwa nguCavin Johnson elibambe ibhuleki kuTop 8.
Lokhu kuyinto eyingqayizivele kwazise eminyakeni edlule obeku

bu alesi sifundazwe ezama ukuvika izembe.
Kulamaqembu yiMaritzburg kuphela ebingeke isaphuthwa yithuba lokungena kuTop 8. I-Lamontville Golden Arrows na-AmaZulu FC ukube bashayiwe bebezozithola besendaweni ebucayi kulogi. Igoli le-AmaZulu FC abedlala neCape Town City eKing Zwelithini Stadium eMlazi, lishaywe nguMbongeni Gumede ngomzuzu wama-63 emuva kwefree kick eshaywe nguJabulani Ncobeni. IGolden Arrows yona ithole iphuzu elilodwa idlala neMaritzburg United ngegoli elishaywe nguLamola ngowama-
...
ge ngomzuzu wama-81. Lo mdlalo ubuseHarry Gwala Stadium.
Ukungena kwalawa maqembu kuTop 8 kuvalele ngaphandle amaqembu asethathwa njenganegunya lokuqeda njalo ebalwa nayisishiyagalombili aphezulu okuyiBidvest Wits yona eguqiswe yiPlatinum Stars ngelilodwa eqandeni (1-0) neSupersport United yona okuthe noma iphumelele ngokushaya iBaroka FC ngelilodwa eqandeni (1-0) kwasho khona ukuthi isikhathi sesihambe kakhulu iphikwa yimiphumela. Iphethe ilele endaweni ye-11 kulogi.

Kubulawe 6 emashini eSudan
2012-08-01 07:16
Khalid Abdelaziz no-Ulf Laessing
Khartoum - Kubulawe abantu abayisithupha ngesikhathi kunombhikisho wokukhalazela ukunyuka kwamanani ezidingongqangi eDarfur, entshonalanga neSudan, kusho izikhulu.
Izishoshovu zisole amaphoyisa ngokusebenzisa izinhlamvu zangempela kulo mbhikisho omkhulukazi obumelene nohulumeni kusukela uMengameli Omar
Hassan al-Bashir amemezela uguquko mayelana nezidingo.
ISudan isenkingeni yezomnotho kusukela iSouth Sudan yathola uzimelegeqe, yathatha iningi lomkhiqizo kawoyela, nokuyiwona omise le minotho yomibili.
Abantu ababalelwa ku-1 000, bebewotha ubomvu bavala nemigwaqo eNyala, kwacekelwa phansi namabhilidi.

Lucky Sithole
Esinye sezizathu ezenza umdlalo wekhilikithi wezinsuku ezinhlanu uhehe kangaka kubalandeli ukuthi umzuzwana owodwa nje wokuthile okwenzeka emdlalweni uvame ukugqama.
Into efana nale yenzeke eKapa ngesikhathi i-India ithola ama-innings esibili emdlalweni wayo wesithathu ibhekene neNingizimu Afrika. Umdlalo ubuhamba kahle nochungechunge belilingana, njengoba womabili amaqembu aseke ayinqoba imdlalo .
UMarco Jansen ubephosa , kanti uCheteshwar Pujara yena ubeshaya. UPujara ushaye ibhola – kwaphenduka kwaba umzuzu omangalisayo. UKeegan Petersen ulule isandla sakhe kwesokudla, umzimba wakhe kanye nengalo wayilula ngokuphelele, wabamba ibhola ngesandla esisodwa.
Kodwa lo mzuzu omangalisayo kwezemidlalo ungase ube ngowesikhashana njengoba inzuzo yama-innings, yomdlalo kanye nochungechunge ivune iNingizimu Afrika.
Njengoba kusasele izinsuku ezimbili, iNingizimu Afrika idinga ukushaya ama-run angaphezudlwana kuka-200 umdlalo ungakapheli. Ukuthi iNingizimu Afrika iyawina noma cha, kungaba umzuzu omkhulu kunayo yonke emsebenzini kaPetersen.

INHLANGANO eyengamele ukhetho, i-Independent Electoral Commission (IEC), inikezwe umnqamulajuqu ngodaba oluthinta icala elifakwe yi-ActionSA.
INkantolo yezoKhetho inikeze i-IEC umnqamulajuqu wakusasa ukuba ifake amaphepha aphikisa isicelo se-ActionSA.
I-ActionSA yanikela kule nkantolo ngesonto eledlule emva kokuthola ukuthi igama layo aliveli emaphepheni okuvota.
Kulesi sicelo i-ActionSA ifuna ukuba le nkantolo ichithe isinqumo se-IEC.
Emaphepheni okuvota kuvela kuphela uphawu lwe-ActionSA kanti
... 
ngoLwesihlanu lwangesonto eledlule, kepha iNkantolo yezoKhetho ithathe isinqumo sokunikeza i-IEC ithuba lokuthi ifake amaphepha aphikisa isicelo se-ActionSA.
Le nkantolo iphinde yanikeza i-ActionSA umnqamulajuqu wangoLwesihlanu ukuba ifake amaphepha azokube ephendula okuqukethwe emaphepheni e-IEC.
Inkantolo iveze ukuthi abekho abantu abazobizwa ukuba bazokwethula ubufakazi kuleli cala, kuzocubungulwa kuphela okuqukethwe emaphepheni afakwe kuyona.
USihlalo we-ActionSA, uMnuz Michael Beaumont, uth
...
ntolo bekungafanele izinhlaka ezithintekayo kulolu daba izinikeze isikhathi eside kangaka ukuba zifake amaphepha.
“Lolu daba luyaphuthuma ngendlela eyisimanga. Lesi sikhathi esinikezwe izinhlaka ezithintekayo ukuba zifake amaphepha asikhombisi ukuthi inkantolo iluthathela phezulu udaba.”
I-ActionSA inokwesabela ukuthi ingase ilahlekelwe yinqwaba yamavoti uma igama layo lingagcina lingafakwanga emaphepheni okuvota njengoba ithi abantu bazokuthola kunzima ukuthola le nhlangano emaphepheni okuvota.

Izici
I-MR5 ingumkhiqizo ojwayelekile wokuphinda usebenzise imabula, ukusetshenziswa njalo ngeke kushintshe ukubukeka kwemabula.
Ubuchwepheshe bokungena kwe-ion obunelungelo lobunikazi obuyingqayizivele benza indawo yemabula ecutshunguliwe ibe mningi kakhulu, iqinile futhi imelane nokugqokwa, futhi "ikhanye kodwa ingasheleli".
Umkhiqizo ungasetshenziselwa wonke amatshe aqukethe i-calcium carbonate ne-magnesium carbonate, njengemabula, i-limestone, imabula yokufakelwa ne-terrazzo.
Incazelo
I-MR5 
... 
wesakhiwo noma ukupholishwa kwezindawo zemabula. Ingashesha ukulungisa imihuzuko eyakhiwe ebusweni bemabula ngokugqoka, ukubuyisela noma ukuthuthukisa isicwebezelisi sendawo. Ukugcinwa njalo kungagcina ukukhanya okuhle isikhathi eside, futhi ngasikhathi sinye kwakha ungqimba lwe-crystal surface shiny, oluqinile. Ibuye isetshenziselwe ukugcina itshe lokufakelwa.
I-Crystallization iyindlela yokwenza kabusha isicwebezelisi samatshe aphansi kwe-calcium afana nemabula, i-limestone ne-travertine, ukwe
...
waphansi futhi iyishaye isebenzisa umshini waphansi ngoboya bensimbi noma iphedi yokupholisha. Umshini ofakwe amapayipi ukhiqiza ukushisa nge-crystallizer, futhi kwakha inhlanganisela entsha phezu kwemabula, yalokhu, ukuvikela imabula ngokugcina umbala wayo ubuna nokugcina ukukhanya kwetshe. Isetshenziselwa ukuhlanza imabula yangaphakathi kuphela futhi kuzo zonke izigaba isesha ukusebenza kwayo njengasemahhovisi, ezitolo ezinkulu, ezakhiweni zomphakathi, emakhaya kanye nasemahhotela.

Uma ungakaze ube neziqubu zegobongo awukaze uzwe ukuvumelana okuthokozisayo kwe-Ndlovu Youth Choir.

Umndeni we-Chaetodontidae wakhiwe mikhakhwo elitjhumi kanye nemihlobo elikhulu netjhumi nane. Mhlobo ojayelekileko nohlukaniseka lula nawuhlangana neemilo zangemanzini. Udla emini begodu ukhamba ibanga elide nawuzumana nokudla. Kanengi uba nombala ofipheleko ebusuku. Ezinye zazo zakha umhlambi, kodwana kanengi zitholakala ngambili. Zimhlobo obekelela amaqanda ngaphakathi komhlobo welwandle elivulekileko (Pelagic spawners).

Esigabeni sendaba eziphathelane lezizalwane zeZimbabwe ezihlala emazweni, lamuhla sixoxe loMnu. Gift Tawanda Marufu, ohlala eBotswana owalinyazwa kakubi ngumqatshi.
UMarufu uthi wayesebenzela uRadihele, eMahalapye, lapho adutshulwa khona edinga ukuthi ahlawulwe iholo lakhe. Wacina equnywa izandla ngenxa yamangxeba abalawo.
Okwamanje uthi lokhe elenhlamvu zombhobho esifubeni ezingakakhitshwa. Uthi usebophisa umqhatshi lo ngoba engesenelisi ukuselela imuli yakhe esihlupheka.
Kasenelisanga ukukhuluma lomqhatshi lo esinikwe ibizo lakhe kodwa esingeke salifaka emphakathini njengoba singakhulumanga laye.
Abazi ngodaba lolu bathi okwehlela uMarufu akutshiyananga lokubhekane lezinye izizalwane zeZimbabwe ezihlala kwamanye amazwe.
UMarufu uthi uthwele nzima ngokuzama ukuphandela imuli yakhe.

Kwasukasukela, kwakukhona izilwane zifuna ukubeka inkosi yazo. Izilwane zonke zanquma umhlangano, emhlanganweni kwathiwa ozobekwa abe iNkosi kumele aqede isaka likapelepele angasho ukuthi, “hl hl hl.” Nangempela yaqala impungushe yaluma owodwa yathi, “hl hl” kwathiwa phuma. Kwalandela indlovu yaluma yathi, “hl hl” kwathiwa phuma. Zalandela zonke izilwane zonke zathi, “hl hl” zabuyiselwa eceleni.
Kwabizwa unogwaja, waluma wathi, “hawu nawe mpungushe ulokhu uthi hl hl umnandi kabi lopelepele.” Waqhubeka wadla unogwaja wathi, “nawe ndlovu ngikwethembile ulingisela umpungushe uthi, hl hl” Aqhubeke unogwaja, “nawe chakide ulokhu uthi hl hl.” Aqhubeke, ayoliqeda isaka unogwaja, eklolodele ezinye izilwane, “bukani mina ngiyaliqeda isaka manje angikasho ukuthi, hl hl.” Wabekwa waba iNkosi unogwaja ngokuhlakanipha kwakhe.
Cosu cosu yaphela.

Johannesburg - Umdlali weMamelodi Sundowns u-Emmanuel Baffour uthe uzokulwela ukuthola indawo isikhathi esithe xaxa uma iqembu lakhe lidlala, kusho umbiko weKickOff.com.
Lo mdlali odabuka eGhana wasayina inkontileka yeminyaka emibili naleli qembu ngaphambi kokuqala kwesizini, wacacisa ukuthi uzoba nenselelo yokuthola ijezi.
UBaffour, 23, akalilahlile ithemba ngokuthi uzogcina esitholile isikhathi sokudlala.
"Ngijabule kuleli qembu, okusele kimina ukuthi ngizibonakalise, ngingafikeli ubala kwelinye izwe."
"Ithuba lami lokuqala leli ngidlala ngaphandle kweGhana futhi ngiyazi izinto zizohamba kahle," ephetha.

IGibela Sport isihabule ngemithombo yayo ethembekile ukuthi imenenja kaDumisani Zuma uzama ngokusemandleni ukutholela lomdlali imvume yokumkhulula eNaturena.
UZuma akabonakali ejimini namanje, kulandela ukumiswa kwakhe ekuzibandakanyeni neqembu ngesizathu sokufika ekhempini yeqembu edle amanzi amponjwana.
Ngesikhathi emiswa uZuma, imenenja yakhe uBasia Michaels yachazela abakwaSABC Sport ukuthi abatshelwanga lutho ngesimemezelo seChiefs.
IChiefs ayiphindanga yakhuluma ngodaba lukaZuma kusukela ngomhlaka 2 kuMeyi. Kuvela ukuthi iChiefs isaqhuba imihlangano ngenhloso yokuqondisa uZwane izigwegwe.
UZuma wamiswa yiGlamour Boys ngoNovemba wangonyaka odlule ngoba wayesolwa ngokufika ejimini ephuzile. Iqembu lakhipha isinqumo sokuthi uZuma athole usizo longoti.
Kuvela ukuthi imenenja kaZuma isiqale izingxoxo neChiefs ngenhloso yokuthola imvume yokumkhulula eqenjini.
Ebuzwa ngodaba lukaZuma, uMichaels ubeke kanje.
“Kunzima ukuphendula lombuzo ngoba abezindaba bajwayele ukukhipha izimemezelo kungakaqinisekiswa lutho. Sisalungisa indaba yokuqondisa kwezigwegwe, ngicela usinikeza isikhathi. Ngiyazi ukuthi isinqumo angeke simjabulise uZuma kodwa kusengenzeka noma yini,” kusho uMichaels.
UMichaels uthi isamcasula indaba yokukhishwa kwesimemezelo ezinkundleni zokuxhumana, ekubeni yena engatshelwanga lutho.
“IChiefs izokwazisa abalandeli uma sekukhishwe isinqumo. Kuyenzeka nathi singatshelwa lutho. Sesilinde isikhathi eside mayelana nodaba lukaZuma,” kusho uMichaels.

Ungagqoka kanjani futhi ukhumule kahle gown?
Inqubo yokuhlukaniswa:
1. Gqoka kusuka phansi kuya phezulu;
2. Donsela ama-cuffs bese uhlela ama-cuffs;
3. Donsa i-zipper phezulu ukuze ulungise ukuqina kwesigqoko;
4. Namathisela uphawu lweVelcro ezingutsheni.
Inqubo ekhungathekisayo:
1. Dabula uphawu lweVelcro ngaphezulu kwezingubo bese unzip ngaphakathi.
2. Donsela isigqoko phezulu uye emuva ukuze ikhanda likhumule nemikhono.
3. Susa umqulu kusuka phezulu kuya phansi.
4. Khumula izingubo zakho, faka uhlangothi olungcolisiwe esikhwameni semfucuza yezokwelapha.

Sphiwe Masilela
Middendorp useqinisekisiwe njengomqeqeshi omusha weMaritzburg United.
Iqembu likhombe indlela uEric Tinkler ngoMsombuluko ekuseni kulandela imiphumela eminingi engemihle.
Sekungokwesithathu uMiddendorp ebuyela eqenjini elizinze eMaritzburg, njengoba kade ephethe izintambo izikhathi ezimbili ezedlule.
Lo Mjalimane ucishe waholela iKaizer Chiefs esicongweni seligi kodwa wehluleka ukujaha isicoco esigcine sithathwe iMamelodi Sundowns abangompetha.
Ku-akhawunti yabo ye-Twitter, iUnited ithe: “Siyakwamukela ekhaya. UErnst Middendorp ubuyile kwi-Team of Choice”.
Lo mqeqeshi odabuka eJalimane usenikwe umsebenzi wokufaka iUnited esicongweni se-DStv Premier League.
Inkinga yakhe yokuqala ubhekene neSupersport United esefomini eHarry Gwala kusasa (ngoLwesihlanu) ebusuku.
Amahlebezi kaMiddendorp okubuyela kwakhe kule kilabhu afike kwezwakala ngesikhathi ecela ukukhululwa kwinkontileka yakhe yeminyaka emithathu nezinkakha ezinkulu zase-Ethiopia iSaint George Sports Club.
Ngemuva kwemidlalo emine yeligi, iMaritzburg ibhajwe ezansi kwe-log ngaphandle kwephuzu.
I-Team of Choice manje isidlale imidlalo engu-11 ngaphandle kokunqoba okubuyela kwiligi ye-bio-bubble ebibanjelwe ukuqedela umkhankaso wezi-2019/2020.
Picture source @MaritzburgUtd

Shijiazhuang G-House Trading Co., Ltd (lokudluliselwa ngokuthi "G-House" ngemuva kwalokhu) kuyinto Chinese professional eyenza imithi isithekelisi elise adumile "Pharma- Capital" of China - Shijiazhuang, Isifundazwe Hebei. G-House isungule yokuthengisa ithimba layo abanolwazi abenza kokudala amabhuloho yokuxhuma izimboni ezenza imithi yasekhaya futhi emakethe kwezilwandle.
G-indlu, kanye namafektri eziningi ezifuywayo zemithi, kuye kubhaliswe amakhulu nemithi emazweni amaningi nge ukhathazekile izidakamizwa ekuphathweni igunya ukuze uthole AMM. Khonamanjalo G-indlu isungule mutual izinzuzo nokubambisana abasabalalisi wendawo yokumaketha. Le mishanguzo bhalisiwe isimo umthamo ithebhulethi, capsule, umjovo wamanzi, powder umjovo, infusions, Syrups, ukumiswa, ukhilimu, iso & ekhaleni lehla, kuyilapho zihlanganisa izidakamizwa Imithi, anti-omsakazo silwanyana, anti-neoplastic, anti-yisinanakazana, antihistamine, isimiso sezinzwa esiyinhloko, umgudu wokuphefumula, isimiso sokugaya ukudla bungene, ama-hormone, ulungise lokudla nokunye.
G-indlu futhi ithumela kwamanye amazwe izinto ezenza imithi eluhlaza, Tinsita Medical Veterinary Izidakamizwa.
QUALITY KAKHULU, SERVICE KAKHULU kuyinto G-house`s isimiso.
G-House ngabomvu kokwenza uphenyo ngokubambisana kusukela izinkampani ohlonishwa emhlabeni wonke.

Umbuso uthi laba ababili, egameni lenkampani kaTshepiso i-Motheko Projects ngokungemthetho baqamba amanga ngemisebenzi yokuhweba yenkampani ngesikhathi beletha amaphepha entela yenkampani ngenhloso yokuqola i-SARS.

a lokukhwabanisa noma ele-Contravention of Tax Administration Act elihlobene nezinkontileka ze-PPE.

bule ngendlela izinto ezihambe ngayo nangendlela esidlale ngayo kulolu hambo. ...
ikhathi imiqondo yethu ihlale isesimeni umdlalo uqala uze uyophela.

Uzobolela ejele owabulala isalukazi
2012-12-14 08:19
Durban - Uzobolela ejele owesilisa waKwaZulu-Natal, nogwetshwe eNkantolo eNkulu yaKwaDukuza ngokubulala owesifazane, kusho amaphoyisa esifundazwe.
USimphiwe Steven Khumalo utholakale enecala lokubulala uThombi Mthabela, 70, ngoFebhuwari 21, kusho uColonel Jay Naicker.
Uphinde wagwetshelwa ukutholakala nesibhamu esingagunyaziwe nezinhlamvu.
UMthabela wayesendleleni eya kwakhe ngabo-15:00 ephuma esitolo eNgulule, enyakatho neMpangeni, ngesikhathi evinjezelwa nguKhumalo.
“UKhumalo wamsola ngokuthakatha nokweba izimbuzi zakubo,” kusho uNaicker.
"Wabe esedubula uMthabela izikhawu eziningana ngaphambi kokubaleka."
UMthabela waphelela endaweni yesehlakalo.

High density Polyethylene Resin
I-HDPE iyi-resin ye-thermoplastic engeyona i-polar ecwebe kakhulu ekhiqizwa nge-copolymerization ye-ethylene kanye nenani elincane le-a-olefin monomer.I-HDPE ihlanganiswa ngaphansi kwengcindezi ephansi futhi ngakho-ke ibizwa nangokuthi i-polyethylene ephansi yokucindezela.I-HDPE ngokuyinhloko iwumugqa wesakhiwo samangqamuzana futhi inamagatsha amancane.Inezinga eliphezulu le-crystallization kanye nokuminyana okuphezulu.Ingakwazi ukumelana namazinga okushisa aphezu
... 
 nezinto eziyisisekelo zokukhiqiza i-polyethylene ene-chlorine.
1. Ibanga Lefilimu ye-HDPE
Ibanga lefilimu le-HDPE lisetshenziswa kabanzi ekukhiqizeni izikhwama zezikibha, izikhwama zokuthenga, izikhwama zokudla, izikhwama zikadoti, izikhwama zokupakisha, ulwelwesi lwezimboni kanye nefilimu ye-multilayer.Ibuye isetshenziswe ekufakweni kwesiphuzo nemithi, ukupakishwa kokugcwalisa okushisayo kanye nokupakishwa komkhiqizo omusha kanye nefilimu ephikisana ne-seepage esetshenziswa kubunjiniyela be-hy
...
oluphindwe kabili, amapayipi anodonga oluyizigodi, amapayipi e-silicon-core, amapayipi okunisela ezolimo kanye namapayipi epulasitiki e-aluminium ayinhlanganisela.Ngaphezu kwalokho, ngokusebenzisa i-extrusion esebenzayo, ingasetshenziselwa ukukhiqiza amapayipi e-polyethylene axhumene (PEX) ukuze ahlinzeke ngamanzi abandayo nashisayo.

Ngokusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe be-quantum bezinkampani zayo ezimbili zabazali, i-Quantinuum ihlela ukunikela ngohlelo oluphelele lwezingxenyekazi zekhompuyutha ze-quantum nesofthiwe, okuhlanganisa nesistimu yokusebenza ye-quantum yokuqala yemboni.

um computing ukunikeza izixazululo zomhlaba wangempela kuwo wonke umuntu. evela kumakhasimende ethu kanye nozakwethu, ”kusho u-Ilyas Khan, umsunguli weCambridge Quantum, ozohola iQuantinuum njenge-CEO.

I-Quantinuum inethemba lokuletha izixazululo ngendlela yokuthi ziham
...
be-software ye-quantum ukufinyelela okuvulekile ku-"tket," ikhithi yokuthuthukisa isoftware ye-quantum ezimele.

Kunezinzuzo eziningana zokusebenzisai-patio ifenisha ihlanganisa.
Nazi ezinye zezinzuzo:
1.Ivikela kuma-elementi:Izembozo zefenisha ye-Patio zinikeza ungqimba lwesivikelo kuzinto zesimo sezulu esibi njengemvula, iqhwa, nelanga, ezingalimaza noma zifiphale ifenisha yakho ngokuhamba kwesikhathi.
2.Yengeza isikhathi sempilo yefenisha yakho:Ngesembozo esivikelayo, ifenisha yakho mancane amathuba okuthi yonakale, okusiza ekwandiseni isikhathi sayo sokuphila.
3. Yonga imali:Ngokutshala imali kumasembozo wefenisha ye-patio, ungonga imali ngokugwema isidingo sokushintsha ifenisha yakho ngenxa yokulimala kwesimo sezulu.
4.Kulula ukuyisebenzisa:Izembozo zefenisha ye-Patio zisebenziseka kalula, ezinamakhava amaningi afaka nezinqubo ezilula zokuzisusa.
5.Igcina ifenisha ihlanzekile:Ngokuvala ifenisha yakho, ungayivikela othulini, ukungcola, nemfucumfucu, okwenza kube lula ukuyihlanza nokuyinakekela.
6.Ithuthukisa ukubukeka kwesikhala sakho sangaphandle:Ngokugcina ifenisha yakho ibukeka kahle, indawo yakho yangaphandle izobukeka imema futhi yamukeleka kakhulu.
Kafushane, ukusebenzisa izembozo zefenisha ye-patio kuyindlela elula nethengekayo yokuvikela ifenisha yakho yangaphandle, ukunweba ubude bayo bempilo, futhi uthuthukise ukubukeka kwendawo yonke yakho yangaphandle.

SKHOSIPHI MTHEMBU
UDOTSWE ngamaphoyisa ngokuthi ayolanda ingane yakhe (12) esiteshini samaphoyisa eNanda – ebiphume iya esikoleni – owesilisa waseDube Village, eNanda, kanti zizomkhalela ngecala lokuyinukubeza.
Lona wesilisa – esingeke simdalule ukuvikela isisulu – uboshwe. Kubikwa ukuthi isigameko sokunukubezwa kwale ngane senzeke ngoLwesine emzini wakhe umsolwa. Ubehlala nayo nonina ongayizali.
Umthombo uhlebele ILANGA ukuthi konke lokhu kuqale ngoLwesithathu olwedlule. Uthi uyise wesisulu uqale wasivalela ekamelweni, wasiphoqa ukuba simdlalise isitho sakhe sangasese. “Ngosuku olulandelayo, uphinde wayibizela egunjini lakhe, wayinukubeza. NgoLwesihlanu ingane ivuke yaya esikoleni, yafike yabikela othisha ukuthi inukubezwe nguyise. Othisha baxhumane namaphoyisa asePhoenix – njengoba isikole sikhona – okuyiwo ahambise ingane eNanda, lapho ihlala kona,” kusho umthombo.
Uthi kuhambe isikhathi kwaze kwaba ntambama umsolwa engayiboni ingane njengoba ibihambe iya esikoleni. Amaphoyisa abe esemshayela ucingo, emtshela ukuthi ingane isesiteshini makayoyilanda, ngokusho komthombo. Uthi umsolwa ufike esiteshini ehamba nesinganina sengane, zamkhalela.
Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uLt-Col Robert Netshiunda, uthe amaphoyisa abophe umsolwa
oneminyaka ewu-38, ngecala lokunukubeza indodakazi yakhe. Uthe ngokombiko, umsolwa ubengaqali ukukwenza lokhu.

Uphiko lwentsha ku-ANC i-ANCYL ithi imzamo yokuphonsela inselelo eNkantolo uMengameli waloluPhiko uMnum Collen Maine imayelana nenkomfa ye-ANC yokuqoka ubuholi bayo ngoZibandlela (December).
Lokhu kuza njengoba labo ababili ebebengamalungu e-ANCYL ngaphambilini besabise ngokuya eNkantolo uma i-ANC ingenzi munyakazo ngoMaine kanye nabanye abaholi baloluPhiko lwentsha ku-ANC abathi imnyaka yabo isedlulile emnyakeni yobudala ekuholeni noma ekubeni ilungu lwaloluPhiko. UMthethosisekelo we-ANCYL uveza ukuthi ubulungu baloluPhiko buphela buphela umangabe umuntu esenemnyaka engaphezulu kuka-35 ubudala.
Owe-ANCYL uNjabulo Nzuza uthi bonke labo abafuna uMaine asule ngoba nakhu esenemnyaka engaphezulu kuka-35 banohlelo lwabo nje olucashile. Uthi bazomvikela uMaine ngoba akusuyena owokuqala ukuthi ahole loluPhiko yize imnyaka yakhe isidlulile kwelindelekile.
LoluPhiko luthi uMaine usazoqhubeka nokuhola inhlangano ngoba nabaholi baloluPhiko abadala benza okufanayo.

Ibandla elibusayo kweleSouth Africa, eleANC, selize lavuma ukuhlawula uhulumende phezu kokusebenzisa indizamtshina yebutho ukuya eZimbabwe ukuyakhulumisana leziphathamandla zeZanu PF ngeviki edluleyo.
Amabandla aphikisayo kulelolizwe yiwo aphoqe iANC ukuthi ihlawule limali ngoba esithi kwakungaqondanga ukuthi iqula lalelibandla lisebenzise indizamtshina kahulumende.
Unobhala jikelele weANC, uMnu Ace Magashule, onguye owayekhokhela iqula elaya eZimbabwe, uxolisile izolo wathi bazahlawula.
Wengeze wathi bahamba ngendizamtshina yebutho ngoba kwakungela ndizamtshina eziya eZimbabwe ngenxa yegciwane leCoronavirus.
Lelibandla lazise njalo ukuthi lizaphindela eHarare maduze ukuyakhulumisana lamabandla aphikisayo lenhlanganiso ezizimeleyo ngokuhluphayo eZimbabwe.
Kodwa ibandla leZanu PF alikufuni lokhu ngoba lithi akuladubo oludinga umlamlankunzi.
Umgcinisihlalo wenhlanganiso emela izizalwane zezwekazi leAfrica ezihlala kweleSouth Africa, eyeAfrican Diaspora Forum, uMnu. Vusumuzi Sibanda utshele iStudio 7 ukuthi uhambo lwequla leli lwamangalisa abantu abanengi ababecabanga ukuthi lihamba limele uhulumende hatshi ibandla leANC.

I-Apex Quartz Stone iyimboni enkulu ye-quartz yobungcweti yama-slabs e-quartz nesihlabathi se-quartz.
Cha, i-quartz itholakala ngezinhlobonhlobo namaphethini.I-quartz ingakwazi ukulingisa i-granite ngokunembile noma elinye itshe.
YEBO.Sicela usithinte uma udinga, amasampula WAMAHHALA ayatholakala, kanye nezindleko zemali yezimpahla ngekhasimende.
Ngokuvamile i-T/T (30% idiphozi / 70% ngaphambi kokulayisha), 100% L/C lapho ubona.
Ungenza inkokhelo ku-akhawunti yethu yasebhange, i-Western Union noma i-PayPal:
Idiphozithi engu-30% kusengaphambili, ibhalansi engu-70% iqhathaniswa nekhophi ye-B/L.
Ngokuvamile, i-quartz ye-APEX ingasetshenziswa isikhathi esingaphezu kweminyaka eyi-15, ngenxa yokuthi ayinazimbobo, ayigobi, imelana nokushayisana, ubufakazi bokuklwejwa, i-eco-friendly futhi idinga nje ukulungiswa.
Singakunikeza intengo yokuphromotha uma inani lifinyelela ngaphezu kweziqukathi ezi-5.
Intengo incike kusayizi, umbala kanye nobunzima benqubo yobuchwepheshe.Ungathintana nomthengisi ukuze uthole imininingwane eyengeziwe.
I-Apex inobunikazi obubodwa bezinkwali zabo nezimboni zokucubungula isihlabathi se-quartz ezivela eFujian, eChina.
Ichweba laseXiamen esifundazweni saseFujian.
I-MOQ yethu ivamise ukuba yi-1x20'GP.
Isikhathi sokulethwa singama-30-45 izinsuku zokusebenza ngemuva kokuthola idiphozi.
Imikhiqizo yethu eyinhloko ihlanganisa imikhiqizo eminingi yamatshe kuyilapho imikhiqizo yethu efakiwe i-Quartz ne-Marble slabs.

Lanxa ukwephulwa kwamalungelo oluntu kuqhubeke kubhahile eZimbabwe nyakenye, elakusasa likhanya lithembisa kulandela ukugenqulwa kombuso kaMnu Robert Mugabe.
Lawa ngamazwi enhlanganiso ekhankasela amalungelo oluntu, iAmnesty International, ewethule eHarare ngoLwesine ngemva kwenholisiso yayo ebiqondane lokulondolozwa kwamalungelo kazulu.
Inhlolisiso le ikhangele njalo isimo samalungelo oluntu emhlabeni jikelele. Emhlubulweni wezansi yezwekazi leAfrica, linhlanganiso ithe abalwela amalungelo bahlukuluzwe kakhulu ngohulumende babo ngo2017.
Umqondisi weAmnesty International eZimbabwe, uMnu Cousin Zilala usole uhulumende weZimbabwe esithi wephula ilungelo loluntu mihla lamalanga lanxa nje ekulandula lokhu.
Kodwa uZilala uthe ukugenqulwa kukaMugabe embusweni libutho nyakenye kulethe ithemba lokuthi ukuhlukuluzwa okugoqela ukubotshwa lokutshaywa kwabantu abaphikisana lohulumende kuzahlehla.
Facebook Forum

Ezinye izizalwane zeZimbabwe zithi ukungahlali phansi kuka Mongameli Robert Mugabe esiya emazweni nsuku zonke, kuphazamisa imihlangano eqhakathekileyo yokubuswa kwelizwe njengoba esehlala engekho ekhaya.
Zithi ilizwe kalisabuswa ngemfanelo.
UMugabe usanda kuvela kweleJapan lapho akade esemhlanganweni weWorld Conference on Disaster Risk Management.
Uthe efika ekhaya wahle walubhekisa kwele Namibia emkhosini wokugcotshwa kukaMongameli Hage Geingob ukuthatha intambo zombuso.
NgoMvulo uMugabe ulubhekisa kwele Algeria ukuyahlangana leziphathamandla zakulelo lizwe. UMugabe uke wethekelela kweleEthiopia ngoZibandlela esamukela isikhundla sikamgcinisihlalo wenhlanganiso yeAfrican Union.
Engakayi kwele Ethiopia uke wayakukhefu lakhe lomnyaka lemmuli yakhe eSingapore. Esuka kwele Ethiopia uphindele kwele eSingapore esiyathatha umkakhe engakalubhekisi kwele Zambia lapho emkhosini wokugcotshwa kukamongameli Edgar Lungu.
Sikhulumanje uMugabe ukhangelelwe ukulubhekisa kwamanye amazwe esevela kwele Algeria phansi kwenhlanganiso yeAfrican Union le SADC.
Omunye walabo abasola okwenziwa nguMugabe, nguMnu. Albert Mhlanga okubandla leMDC-Renewal othi imihlangano yonke eqakathekileyo isimisiwe yikungahlali phansi kukaMugabe.
Kodwa-ke umsekeli webandla leZanu PF, uMnu. Fidelis Fengu njalo oyingcwethi kwezombusazwe utshele uGibbs Dube ukuthi uMugabe uqhuba owakwetheswa nguzulu owamkhethayo kukhetho lukamongameli ngomnyaka ka2013.

Ngenxa yokuphrinta kwe-UV ngaphezulu, amaphaneli ezimpawu ze-NEWCOBOND anamandla amahle kakhulu okunamathela kuyinki wokuphrinta angaqinisekisa ukuqina kwemiklamo yokukhangisa.
Iphaneli yezimpawu ze-NEWCOBOND isebenzise izinto ezibalulekile ezimsulwa ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukucaba nokuhlanzeka kwendawo, awekho amabhamuza noma amachashazi ngaphezulu.
I-NEWCOBOND ACP inamandla amahle nokuvumelana nezimo, kulula ukuyiguqula, ukusika, ukugoqa, ukubhola, ukujika nokuzifaka.
Ukwelashwa okungaphezulu ngesicelo se-polyester engamelana ne-ultraviolet (ECCA) yezinga eliphezulu, isiqinisekiso seminyaka engu-8-10;uma usebenzisa upende we-KYNAR 500 PVDF, oqinisekisiwe iminyaka eyi-15-20.

Ukuhunyushwa kwephupho mayelana namaphela
Ukubona amaphela emaphusheni, ikakhulukazi lawo avela ebusuku, angathwala izincazelo ezahlukene ezihlobene nempilo yomuntu siqu kanye nemizwelo yomphuphi. Kwezinye izincazelo, lezi zinambuzane zingase zibonakale njengophawu lomuntu onezinhloso ezingcolile, ongase abe nomthelela omubi empilweni yomuntu ophuphayo, okubangela ukukhathazeka nokuphazamiseka ngenxa yenkulumo embi nokuhleba.
Ensizwa engashadile ebona iphela ephusheni layo, lokhu kungase kuhunyu
... 
e futhi athathe izinyathelo ezidingekayo ukuze azivikele emiphumeleni yalomona, njengokusho njalo ukunxusa nokukhipha amademoni ukuze afune isivikelo saphezulu.
Amaphela angena emzimbeni ephusheni angase asho ukuthi umphuphi uyagula noma uhileleke ebuhlotsheni nabantu abangambangela izinkinga nokulimaza. Ukuvela kwamaphela emzimbeni kubonisa ukuqeda umona, ukuphulukiswa kwezifo, ngaphezu kokukhipha abantu abanobuthi noma ukusika ubuhlobo nabo ngemva kwesikhathi sobunzima.
Lapho umuntu ebona amap
...
a kuye ukucabanga kahle.
Uma ubona iphela elibheke phansi elifile, lokhu kumemezela ukusondela kokunqoba izithiyo zamanje nokungena esigabeni sokuzinza nokuthula.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukubona leli phela linomuzwa wokudabuka kubonisa ukuthi izinselele zesikhathi esizayo zingayishintsha kakhulu inkambo yokuphila komphuphi.
Kodwa-ke, uma umuzwa ohambisana nombono uyinjabulo, ikakhulukazi entombazaneni engashadile, khona-ke lokhu kuphakamisa ukuphumelela okubonakalayo kanye nentuthuko emkhathizwe.

i baningi abantu abakhombisa intshisekelo yokupheka, ngakho ngiye ngihambele izindawo ezihlukene, lapho engifike ngicije khona abantu ngokushaya ibhodwe,” kusho uNksz uMseleku.

holakala kuyona zonke izibiliboco zayo.

Lo mqhudelwano wathi abasebenzi bawo bazobhekelelwa ngemuva kweNdebe yoMhlaba kodwa lokho akwenzekanga, kubika i-The Guardian.
Idlanzana labasebenzi abakaze bahole selokhu i-Argentina yaphakamisa isicoco ngoZibandlela.
Abasebenzi baphoqeleke ukuthi bacele imali emakhaya abo e-Afrika.

... 
wayele ukudla kathathu ngosuku ekhaya kodwa lapha kunzima ukudla ngisho nakanye ngosuku. Bengilokhu ngishayela ucingo abangani bami base-Nigeria ngibacela ukuthi bangisize. Selokhu ngafika kulelizwe angikaze ngihole nakanye. Sonke siyazisola ngokuza lapha,” kusho umsebenzi wase-Nigeria.
Onogada baphinde bagqamisa izinkinga zabo zezimali ngemuva kweNdebe yoMhlaba njengoba abanye bethola u-R8 kuphela ngehora.
“Isimo sesisibi kakhulu. Manje bayasijezisa,” kusho omunye unogada.
Onogada bathi ngapham
...
yakenye emakethe yezabasebenzi yase-Qatar licacile kubo bonke abantu,” kusho okhulumela leli hhovisi.
“Abasebenzi abaningi bahlomulile kulezi zinguquko njengokususwa kwezimvume zokuphuma kanye nenkululeko yokushintsha imisebenzi, ukwethulwa kweholo eliphansi lokuqala elingacwasi, ukwenziwa ngcono kwamazinga ezempilo nokuphepha kanye nokufinyelela okungcono kwezobulungiswa.”

Ibandla eliphikisayo ele People's Democratic Party (PDP) ngoLwesine lenze umhlangano wedale lalo laphezulu owe General Council obuhlanganiswe lowe Congress yokukhetha inkokheli ukuze lenelise ukuvala izikhexhe ezavuleka ngemva kokusuka kwamanye amalunga abandla leli.
Umbuthano lo uhlanganise abalandeli bePDP abavele ezabelweni zonke zelizwe, umkhokheli webandla leli uNkosikazi Lucia Matibenga, umongameli webandla leNational People’s Party uNkosikazi Joyce Mujuru kanye lomsekeli wakhe uMnu. Samuel Siphepha Nkomo.
Injongo yalumhlangano bekuyikukhetha inkokheli kanye lokubethula kubalandeli bebandla labo. Abakhethwe emhlanganweni lo abalezikhundla eziphezulu ngumsekeli kamongameli wePDP uMnu. Benson Ntini kanye lomgcinisikhwama uMnu. Trevor Johns.
UNtini uthi wamukele ngenjabulo ukukhethwa kwakhe kodwa uzwa ethwele ijogwe elinzima.
Omunye umlandeli webandla leli, uMnu. Fortune Mlalazi, uthe bayajabula ukubona ibandla lePDP likhula.
Lokhu kusekelwe nguNkosikazi Ottilia Sibanda laye uncome ibandla lePDP esithi lilokuthula njalo bakhangelele ukunqoba okulesisindo bekhokhelwa nguNkosikazi Joice Mujuru.
Ibandla lePDP liyingxenye yomanyano wePeople’s Rainbow Coalition ekhokhelwa nguNkosikazi Joice Mujuru, okhulume emhlanganweni lo esithi umanyano lo uzanqoba njalo uzalwisa ukuthuthukisa iziqinti lapho okuhlala khona uzulu.

Kulandela isinqumo sikahulumende esokuthi angcwabe kutsha ababhubha ngesikhathi seGukurahundi, abanye bathi ngabe uqala axolise andubana loluhlelo luqhutshwe.
Lokhu kulandela umhlangano osanda ukuqhutshwa ngumphathintambo kahulumende obona ngokwenzakala elizweni uMnu. Kazembe Kazembe kanye lenhlanganiso yeMatabeleland Collective.
UMnu. Kazembe ubikwa echasise ukuthi uhulumende useloba imithetho yoku ngcwaba kutsha ababhubha ngalesi isikhathi, wagcizelela ukuthi abangela ncwadi zokuzalwa ngenxa yeGukurahundi bazazithola lula.
Uhlelo lolu luzaqhutshwa yinhlanganiso yeNational Peace and Reconciliation Committee njalo uhulumende uthi usexoxisane lezinduna leyinye inkokheli yezigaba ngaloludaba.
Ukuhlaziya loludaba, sixoxa loMfundisi Anglistone Sibanda.
Siphinde saxoxa loMnu. Joseph Tshuma ilunga lebandla leZANU PF ukuze sizwe imbono yakhe ngaloludaba.

Lesi yisimiso uNkulunkulu asebenza ngaso eNkathini Yezwi. be yinyama womuntu ukuze akhulume ngezindlela ezahlukene, ehlomisa umuntu ukuthi abone uNkulunkulu ngeqiniso, oyiZwi elivela enyameni, nangobuhlakani nezimangaliso Zakhe. Umsebenzi onjalo wenzelwe ukufinyelela kangcono emigomweni yokunqoba umuntu, yokumphele
... 
a oNgcwele phezu kwenu nokuthi ningalidla nliiphuze kanjani izwi likaNkulunkulu ngempumelelo. Ngemva kwesikhathi sokuhlola okunjalo, nizongena eqinisweni lezwi likaNkulunkulu. Uma kuphela wenze isinqumo sokusebenzisana uzokwamukela umsebenzi kaMoya oNgcwele.
Kunezinto ezimbili emgomweni wokudla nokuphuza izwi likaNkulunkulu: Omunye uhambelana nolwazi, omunye ukungena. Imaphi amazwi okufanele uwazi? Ufanele ukwazi amazwi ahambelana nombono (okusho ukuthi, iyiphi iminyaka uNkulukulu asengene kuyo

khanyeni kukaNkulunkulu. Umsebenzi lowo uNkulunkulu azowenza kule minyaka yamanje kanye nokuguquka komsebenzi Wakhe, konke kungatholakala ezwini Lakhe. Uma ungafundi izwi Lakhe, ngeke uqonde lutho. Ngokudla nangokuphuza ezwini Lakhe, ngokuhlanganyela nabazalwane nolwazi lwakho, ulwazi lwakho lwezwi likaNkulunkulu luzophelela. Yile ndlela ongakwazi ngayo ukuliphila empilweni yangempela.

IMeya yomasipala uMtubatuba uVelangenkosi Gumede uthi ufuna ukubuyisa esithinzi ebholeni kulendawo
IMEYA ku masipala waseMtubatuba enyakatho nesifundazwe iKwaZulu-Natali uCllr Velangenkosi Gumede uthi bafuna ukubuyisa isithunzi sale ndawo kwezikanobhutshuzwayo ngokuthi bakhiqize abadlali abazobonakala esigabeni esikhokhelwayo.
“Ukuthuthukisa ibhola kungezinye zezinto esizibeke eqhulwini njengoba sethula uhlahlo mali lukamasipala lwalo nyaka. Kunemali esiyibekele ukuthuthukisa ibhola kwintsha esakhula,” kusho uGumede.
Indawo yaseMtubatuba ingenye yezindawo ehamba phambili ngokukhiqiza ikhono emdlalweni wamankomane njengoba isikhiqize amabhokisa anjengo Innocent “Tycoon” Mantengu, Sboniso Gonya kanye nabanye abaningi.
Lo masipala ubeke imali elinganiselwa ku-R500 000 wezinkulungwane zamarandi ozosetshenziswa kwiMayoral Cup. Ngaphandle kwalo mqhudelwano kuzophinde kubizwe labo abahlonza ikhono ebholeni abavela ezigabeni ezikhokhelwayo ukuze intsha ikwazi ukuzibonakalisa phambi kwabo.
“Sifuna kuphume abadlali lapha abazogijima emaqenjini amakhulu ezigabeni zebhola elikhokhelwayo. Siyazi ikhono likhona kuphela lidinga ukuvezwa, kuyishwa ukuthi uMtubatuba umkhulu kangaka akekho umdlali ogijima esigabeni esikhokhelwayo, ” kuphethe uGumede.

2022 I-Shenzhen International Wireless Charging Technology kanye noMbukiso wesicelo
I-Shenzhen International Wireless Charging Technology kanye ne-Application Exhibition yango-2022 izomema abaholi nabamele izinhlangano zezimboni ezifanele ukuba bawuhambele. Amabhizinisi angama-100 aphezulu embonini avela emazweni nasezifundeni ezingaphezu kuka-30 azobamba iqhaza kulo mbukiso, futhi kulindeleke ukuthi abathengi abangamaShayina nabakwamanye amazwe abayizi-100,000 bazohlangana e-WCT-EXPO, nendawo yombukiso isiyonke engamamitha-skwele ayi-100,000. Abasebenzisi bayahlangana, bakhulise ngokuhlanganyela ivolumu yebhizinisi, badale inani, babonise inani lakho lokubonisa, futhi bavumele umkhiqizo wakho usabalale emhlabeni wonke! Abakhiqizi nabangaphakathi embonini bamukelekile ukukhombisa nokuvakashela.
Indawo yombukiso icishe ibe ngamamitha-skwele ayi-100,000
Cishe ababukeli abangu-3000
Inani lamazwe nezifunda ezibambe iqhaza lidlula ama-30
Amapheshana kazwelonke nawesifunda: Germany, South Korea, Italy, United Kingdom, France, United States, Turkey, India, Japan and Taiwan, njll.
Inani labavakashi abangochwepheshe kulindeleke ukuthi licishe libe ngu-25,000 emazweni nasezifundeni ezingaphezu kuka-20.
Cishe imidiya yokubambisana yezimboni engu-300 evela emazweni angaphezu kuka-20 nezifunda emhlabeni jikelele ikhuthaza futhi ibike kabanzi ngayo yonke inqubo, futhi ijabulela ithonya lemibukiso yomkhiqizo.

Impendulo yalo mbuzo inzima. Kwabanye abantu, kungase kungabi ku-phephile ukudalula kudokotela wabo, ikakhulu emazweni lapho i-LGBT engekho emthethweni noma ubumfihlo phakathi kukadokotela nesiguli akuqinisekisiwe ngumthetho.
Kodwa-ke, uma sikwazi ukwethemba abahlinzeki bethu bezokwelapha, bazokwazi ukusinakekela kangcono. Ukukhuluma nabo mayelana nobunikazi bakho, ukuziphatha ngokocansi, nezinhlobo zobulili onakho kuzobavumela ukuba benze ukuhlolwa okuqondile okudingayo ukuze kugcine unempilo.
Khumbula ukuthi ufanelwe nesipiliyoni ehhovisi likadokotela elingaphephile kodwa futhi likhululekile. Uma udokotela ezama ukukutshela ukuthi ukuziphatha kwakho ngokocansi, ukubonakala kobulili, noma ubulili obunayo akulungile, mtshele ngokuzithoba ukuthi ungathanda ukukhuluma kuphela ngemithi ngenkathi uvakashele.
Hlola le vidiyo eyodwa ngomzuzu e-suka e-Greater Than AIDS ukuze uthole okuningi. (Xhumana nomthombo wezinhlelo zesiNgisi)
